{"tid":1374205,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人人都可以做旗手,只要係你手機開旗既顏色再向上舉比後面睇就可以","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T18:42:09.000Z","uid":48981,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cdadad6c69f3cf0c564d00ebd22eecb42114092c","tid":1374205,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"對面差佬見到你一班人舉高手機又唔知你咩旗,一定嚇到瀨屎<br />\n<br />\n人人做旗手就可以阻止左膠混入舉散水旗<br />\n<br />\n當你一見到前排就統一顏色既出現,就打開手機舉埋一份,好快就可以比到最後排知咩事"},{"pid":"c5195ae0db7c660e6b4222924008ca3e12202d4f","tid":1374205,"uid":97523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"不如咁<br />\n再簡化少少<br />\n<br />\n前進 停 後退<br />\n其實手勢大叫都做到<br />\n好難下下拎部手機出黎<br />\n<br />\n但如果去到撤退時<br />\n用手機電筒向後照<br />\n燈海話比大家知要撤"},{"pid":"e49688aceaea8a51dd4c55f633a792cf8b0b9db4","tid":1374205,"uid":48981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c5195ae0db7c660e6b4222924008ca3e12202d4f","tid":1374205,"uid":97523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"不如咁<br />\n再簡化少少<br />\n<br />\n前進 停 後退<br />\n其實手勢大叫都做到<br />\n好難下下拎部手機出黎<br />\n<br />\n但如果去到撤退時<br />\n用手機電筒向後照<br />\n燈海話比大家知要撤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"舉旗一定需要,因為依家個問題係中排有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鬼</span></strong></strong></span>亂咁叫人散水,但如果係前排舉咗旗,而又無人阻止,姐係枝旗係前排共識,大家就應該跟住前線行動,為咗令訊息一口氣傳去後面,一定要中間每個人都做同一樣野,咁D<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鬼</span></strong></strong></span>就無得亂咁叫人散水"},{"pid":"0b46f42458827d11d19cc8ee5a9c7db8a5a4fd54","tid":1374205,"uid":145377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a156cde71041d7e968ef58f9bf0a0050423882ed","tid":1374205,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16a49257efba1f1bdb1a022eab9d3346cfd3ca99","tid":1374205,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"同黑警纏緊邊得閒攞電話出黎呀<br />\n仲要戴住手套咁唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e138066d9785dd287817d34d1d19bbb514826f0","tid":1374205,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a49257efba1f1bdb1a022eab9d3346cfd3ca99","tid":1374205,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"同黑警纏緊邊得閒攞電話出黎呀<br />\n仲要戴住手套咁唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:53:19.000Z","msg":"對恃個陣大家都鳩流流無野做,呢個時候D鬼就會衝出黎叫散水,你一早舉定大家心中有數就唔會比散水論影響到,而且唔係舉完即做件事"},{"pid":"13b53bd023b38497099266f645e83886bb01aa4e","tid":1374205,"uid":290854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"搵人整旗做旗手啦！"},{"pid":"83477c033da3447c9aa7283865083bb56ac9a60c","tid":1374205,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:38:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29f953953f3619800e7276a251e08cede179494c","tid":1374205,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"[提防散水撚]利用旗手統一宣示前線所有決定<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非最終決定, 勿亂傳</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9WfOGAy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9WfOGAy.png&h=12acc8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線二三排, 搵兩三個, 係前線決定後舉前線旗, <br />\n後面Relay旗,只有線見到前面有統一色旗先好舉, <br />\n見人亂舉就輕輕力屌一下,<br />\n<br />\n旗用紙做<br />\n前線 a2/a3/ 60x30cm布<br />\nRelay a4/a5<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1k6FgMW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1k6FgMW.png&h=712c3d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/PBnJeBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBnJeBY.png&h=0eaa0ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用簡單字色, 傳最重要前線決定<br />\n有咩事睇旗做人，唔洗理其他人講咩<br />\n前線決定就放左係到，自己決定點做<br />\n<br />\n先做好前中後線溝通,用搞掂一條線,線同線間先可以做得更好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旗手會企係前線,當前線手足有統一意見時,旗手就會係前線準許下舉旗<br />\n<br />\n中排既人見到該旗之顏色時,開著手機調整至旗既顏色再向上舉比後面睇或者舉relay旗<br />\n<br />\n每一個人都係中繼旗手,以防有人舉第隻色混淆視聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f7c2091a6c8a9c5d250abf422dc3be466bc176","tid":1374205,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:42:09.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}